'''Marc Grégoire (Tefal)''' was the inventor of [[Non-stick pans|nonstick pans]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.leparisien.fr/economie/a-60-ans-tefal-est-toujours-au-poele-22-01-2017-6601095.php|title=A 60 ans, Tefal est toujours au poêle|date=2017-01-22|work=leparisien.fr|access-date=2018-11-06|language=fr}}</ref> When his wife learned of an [[ONERA]] [[engineer]] using [[Teflon]] to assist in the removal of glass fibre moulds, she challenged him to create some non-stick cookware. He attached Teflon to the base of an [[Aluminium|aluminum]] frying pan.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://montrealgazette.com/technology/science/the-right-chemistry-teflon-coated-happy-pan-brought-joy-then-concerns|title=The Right Chemistry: Teflon-coated 'Happy Pan' brought joy, then concerns|date=2015-05-09|work=Montreal Gazette|access-date=2018-11-06|language=en-US}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=http://byyourside.tefal.com/news/know-invented-non-stick-pan_1335|title=Do you know who invented the non-stick pan ? - Tefal By Your Side|date=2014-11-12|work=Tefal By Your Side|access-date=2018-11-06|language=en-US}}</ref> It was Grégoire who found a way to bond [[Ptfe|PTFE]] to aluminum creating the first ever nonstick cookware<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://home.howstuffworks.com/nonstick-cookware1.htm|title=How Nonstick Cookware Works|date=2008-12-30|work=HowStuffWorks|access-date=2018-11-06|language=en}}</ref> (in 1954)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://babyfair.supermom.com.sg/tefal.html|title=Tefal|website=Baby-English|language=en|access-date=2018-11-06}}</ref> which later became the world leader in nonstick pans.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.ledauphine.com/haute-savoie/2017/05/02/avec-la-poele-du-futur-tefal-continue-d-innover|title=Avec la poêle du futur, Tefal continue d’innover|access-date=2018-11-06|language=fr}}</ref> In 1956<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9eIxAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT162&lpg=PT162&dq=Marc+Gr%C3%A9goire+tefal+date+of+birth&source=bl&ots=rghOmzmiLM&sig=yJpCpXtIMbqOF8wmbe6INDhQj00&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj-1dCUpr_eAhWhuFkKHU_-DzQQ6AEwFHoECAAQAQ#v=onepage&q=Marc%20Gr%C3%A9goire%20tefal%20date%20of%20birth&f=false|title=Strategic Management of Innovation and Design|last=Masson|first=Pascal Le|last2=Weil|first2=Benoît|last3=Hatchuel|first3=Armand|date=2010-09-09|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=9781139915595|language=en}}</ref> Grégoire and his wife launched the Tefal Corporation<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://home.howstuffworks.com/nonstick-cookware1.htm|title=How Nonstick Cookware Works|date=2008-12-30|work=HowStuffWorks|access-date=2018-11-06|language=en}}</ref> developing the slogan: ''La Poêle Tefal, la poêle qui n’attache vraimant pas (The Tefal saucepan, the saucepan pan that really doesn’t stick.'')<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VFExDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT625&lpg=PT625&dq=Marc+Gr%C3%A9goire+tefal+date+of+birth&source=bl&ots=fzXEmqDw5z&sig=efjpADWuWdoc4J-EbG0wrzo8bdI&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj-1dCUpr_eAhWhuFkKHU_-DzQQ6AEwFXoECAcQAQ#v=onepage&q=Marc%20Gr%C3%A9goire%20tefal%20date%20of%20birth&f=false|title=A Dictionary of Modern Design|last=Woodham|first=Jonathan|date=2016-05-19|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=9780192518538|language=en}}</ref> In 2018 it is still regarded as one of the best non-stick pans.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/extras/indybest/house-garden/kitchen-accessories/best-non-stick-frying-pans-reviews-ceramic-for-induction-hobs-pfoa-pfte-brand-a6746391.html|title=What happened when we tried a frying pan enhanced with diamonds|work=The Independent|access-date=2018-11-06|language=en-GB}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/foodanddrink/10708056/Sticking-it-to-non-stick-pans.html|title=Sticking it to non-stick pans|last=Wilson|first=Bee|date=2014-03-21|access-date=2018-11-06|language=en-GB|issn=0307-1235}}</ref>

